92-	// into parallelSpecular[0]/dot3 and the next two directionals BY DIFFUSE INTENSITY into
93-	// parallel[0],[1]; the asset VS's MAIN diffuse term sums parallel[0]+parallel[1] (the
94-	// fill + bounce lights), NOT the sun. D3D11 captured only the first T_parallel -> walls lit
